  "title": "Maintenance Technician- Tai Seng",
  "description": "<p>Job Description &amp; Requirements<br>\nMaintenance Technician<br>\n<br>\nBasic Salary: $2600-$3000 (Gross salary around $3000-$3800)<br>\n<br>\nLocation: Tai Seng<br>\n<br>\n<br>\nRoles &amp; Responsibilities:<br>\n<br>\nJob Description<br>\n<br>\nHandle Building maintenance, upgrading and repair of our amenities and facilities including power distribution systems, ACMV, fire protection systems, plumbing and sanitary and compressed air systems etc.<br>\nConduct regular inspections of the facility, safety hazards, and cleanliness concerns.<br>\nCoordinate and perform basic to intermediate repairs and adjustments to maintain a safe and well-maintained working environment.<br>\nMaintain / Troubleshoot production machinery and equipment to ensure minimal break down and down time of the equipment by problem identification<br>\nPerform routine checks, maintenance, improvement and upgrading of machineries and equipment, perform routine inspections, preventive maintenance, and able to repair basic equipment including mechanical and electrical systems.<br>\nMaintain accurate records of maintenance activities, repairs, and replacements.<br>\nAssist in the installation and setup of new equipment, machinery, or systems.<br>\n<br>\n<br>\nJob Requirements<br>\n<br>\n* Possess NITEC in Building, Electrical, Mechanical, Mechatronics or its equivalent<br>\n<br>\n* Minimum 2 years of hands-on experience in maintenance and repair work in manufacturing industry<br>\n<br>\n* PC literate (MS Office)<br>\n<br>\n* Require to be on standby call<br>\n<br>\n* 5days work week, willing to do overtime if required</p>",
